{"tid":2142612,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實歐聯算唔算係都講求運氣同埋格食格？","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T14:09:33.000Z","uid":60402,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6951dd1290451dc10f73119c725f82517676834f","tid":2142612,"uid":60402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:50:26.000Z","msg":"全盛巴塞地上最強 但都唔可以年年屈歐聯<br />\n哥狗曼城 巴黎又係屈機 點知年年都柒 連歐聯決賽都未入過<br />\n永遠嗰年歐聯嘅大熱門都係滑鐵盧 所以歐聯算唔算係隊波有實力都未必攞到？<br />\n<br />\n另外聯賽+歐聯要一齊拎又係好難<br />\n利物浦聯賽亞軍就拎歐聯 今年超班奪冠就早早出局<br />\n皇馬連續三年歐聯咁癲但又拎唔晒西甲<br />\n熱刺歐聯亞軍但英超得第4<br />\n車仔拎歐聯嗰年英超又只係得第6<br />\n祖記呀 巴黎呀 拜仁呀 近呢十年長期屈聯賽但係得拜仁拎過歐聯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我獌三冠王真係好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb8199ec57af56960b5fcc0384149b7571558fa","tid":2142612,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"今季都係，曼城英超亞軍拎歐聯"},{"pid":"34be2c556b62c10d9870e29a4cb1a645b8017795","tid":2142612,"uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"大部分對賽運動都係咁架啦"},{"pid":"5807582c083cf97bbe433c528a2fb66ed82545ad","tid":2142612,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"巴塞6冠王+5冠班"},{"pid":"500c7550e49599da9aadbc287b3fd86e5d2f26ff","tid":2142612,"uid":119591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:09:33.000Z","msg":"疤果陣買電視機都破產咁濟<br />\n之後幾年西甲球證平啲 所以淨係拎到西甲"}]}